dc_title_s: Map of the Upper portion of the Tuscarawas River Basin showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"|Scale bar lower left corner of map.|Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the upper Tuscarawas River and Chippewa Creek Basins and quality of underground water.
